<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.FilterDevicesWithoutAllFeatures" Title="FilterDevicesWithoutAllFeatures method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator">IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    FilterDevicesWithoutAllFeatures
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterDevicesWithoutAllFeatures</TypeRef> method removes all <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice">IGraphicsDevice</PageRef>
      objects from the current filtered device set, which do not support all the specified <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.Feature">Feature</PageRef>s.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void FilterDevicesWithoutAllFeatures(const std::set<IGraphicsDevice::Feature>& featureSet);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="std::set&lt;IGraphicsDevice::Feature&gt;!cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.Feature" Name="featureSet">
          The set of features to test for support for in the filtered device set
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
